AUDIENCE: Are you going
to autograph the books?

00:23:42.370 --> 00:23:44.453
RACHEL SEARLES: Am I going
to autograph the books?

00:23:44.453 --> 00:23:46.016
Yes, I will.

00:23:46.016 --> 00:23:47.492
You?

