This was the first book
I ever actually finished,

00:23:52.720 --> 00:23:55.730
and I was describing
how long it took me.

00:23:55.730 --> 00:23:58.370
It took me, overall, maybe four
years to write the whole thing.

00:23:58.370 --> 00:23:59.828
I've written the
second book since,

00:23:59.828 --> 00:24:01.590
because there's a
sequel, but I wrote

00:24:01.590 --> 00:24:05.241
that one in about four
months last summer.

00:24:05.241 --> 00:24:05.740
Yes?

